# Contributing

## Local Workflow

```bash
make bootstrap
make unittest
make docs
make package
{% if with_pyinstaller %}make build{% endif %}
```

## Notes

- Keep `CLAUDE.md` and `AGENTS.md` aligned by editing `CLAUDE.md` and running
  `make sync_guides`.
- Keep dependency groups in their corresponding `requirements-*.txt` files.
- Prefer preserving the existing `Makefile`-driven developer entrypoints.

